Git flow
graph TD
    main(main/master) -->|after deployment| develop(develop)
    main -->|prod issue fixes| hotfix(hotfix)
    develop -->|cut release branch once feature is ready for UAT| release(release)
    release --> main
    release -->|UAT issue fixes| feature(Feature Branch)
    develop --> f1(feature/feature1)
    develop --> f2(feature/featureN)
    
    %% Positioning
    subgraph Main Branches
        main
        hotfix
    end
    
    subgraph Development Branches
        develop
    end
    
    subgraph Release Branches
        release
        feature
    end
    
    subgraph Feature Branches
        f1
        f2
    end
    
    %% Layout adjustments
    style main fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style develop fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style release fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style hotfix fill:#ffb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style feature fill:#fbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style f1 fill:#fbb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style f2 fill:#fbb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

